{
  "stem": "2684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And on the left hand side was our set of barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was in block 11 because that was the children barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the gypsy lager was something strange.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were gypsies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They came to us, to our side, and they were dealing with cigarettes because cigarettes was more than food, everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then, little bread and whatever it was to make our life livable, or at least we ate something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we could not go over to their place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And by the time when we arrived, the whole life of the barracks was organized.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Every lager had a-- every block had a block altester, which meant the elder, block elder, or whatever it is-- a Hungarian, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we lived in a barrack, where, if it's suitable for 200 people, it was 1,000.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was suitable for 1,000, we were 4,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "All we knew, we couldn't lie down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were sitting like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the next guy was sitting against our leg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so, and so, and so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One night, everybody into the barracks, big commotion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the barracks had windows-- but not windows, like in a cell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these taller people looked out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, something happening in the gypsy lager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's happening in the gypsy lager.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And next morning, we look over to the other side of the creek, or embankment, or something, and the gypsy lager was empty.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by lunch time, we knew, because you could smell it, that all gypsies had been cremated by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you go in the back there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think-- so he's there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went back, and I met this gentleman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It will come during my speech.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The name will come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
